---
import Card from "../components/card.astro";
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Commissions">
    <div
        class="grow h-full gap-5 flex flex-col w-full max-w-[1000px] items-center"
    >
        <div class="p-5 h-full w-full flex flex-col gap-2">
            <h3 class="antialiased font-sans font-extrabold text-4xl">
                Enjoy a 2% Fixed Fee for Life!
            </h3>
            <p>
                Start building your business with us today! We are committed to
                transparency and simplicity, which is why we charge a fixed fee
                of only 2% on every transaction. There are no hidden fees, and
                we cover the blockchain transaction costs, ensuring that you
                keep more of your earnings.
            </p>
            <h4 class="font-sans font-bold text-2xl mt-4">Why Choose Us?</h4>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-5">
                <li>
                    <strong>Secure Transactions:</strong> Your payments are processed
                    with the highest level of security, ensuring that both you and
                    your customers can transact with confidence.
                </li>
                <li>
                    <strong>No KYC Requirements:</strong> We respect your privacy.
                    You can start accepting payments without the hassle of lengthy
                    identity verification processes.
                </li>
                <li>
                    <strong>Fixed Fee Structure:</strong> With our 2% fixed fee,
                    you can easily calculate your costs and plan your budget without
                    worrying about fluctuating rates.
                </li>
                <li>
                    <strong>No Account Required:</strong> Get started immediately
                    without the need to create an account. Our seamless integration
                    allows you to begin accepting payments right away.
                </li>
                <li>
                    <strong>Instant Payment Verification:</strong> Enjoy real-time
                    payment confirmations, allowing you to serve your customers quickly
                    and efficiently.
                </li>
                <li>
                    <strong>Dedicated Support:</strong> Our team is here to assist
                    you every step of the way, ensuring that you have the support
                    you need to succeed.
                </li>
                <li>
                    <strong>Flexible Integration:</strong> Our payment gateway easily
                    integrates with various e-commerce platforms, making it simple
                    to start accepting Monero payments.
                </li>
            </ul>
            <p class="mt-4">
                Join us and take advantage of a payment solution that
                prioritizes your business's growth and success. Together, we can
                pave the way for a more secure and private payment experience!
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>
